            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_1">This dashboard tracks relative momentum across the 11 GICS sectors for both <strong>US</strong> (SPDR ETFs) and <strong>EU</strong> (STOXX 600). Automated daily scans rank sectors by momentum strength, detect trend shifts, and surface entry and exit setups.</p>
