            <h2 data-i18n="guide_modal_title_2">The Leaderboard</h2>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_2">Your home screen. Every sector is ranked by <strong>composite score</strong> &mdash; a cross-sectional z-score blending:</p>
            <ul data-i18n-html="guide_modal_list_2">
              <li><strong>Level</strong> &mdash; current momentum strength (returns, MA structure, OBV trend)</li>
              <li><strong>Change</strong> &mdash; whether momentum is accelerating or decelerating</li>
              <li><strong>Data</strong> &mdash; signal completeness; sectors with gaps are penalized</li>
            </ul>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_2b">Zero means average across sectors; +1.0 is one standard deviation above. Click any row for the full signal breakdown.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

