            <div class="guide-eyebrow" data-i18n="guide_modal_eyebrow_3">Most actionable signal</div>
            <h2 data-i18n="guide_modal_title_3">Trend Badges</h2>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_3">Computed from rank slope over the last 3&ndash;5 scans. A falling rank number means the sector is climbing the leaderboard.</p>
            <ul data-i18n-html="guide_modal_list_3">
              <li><span class="signal-hi">↑↑ Rising fast</span> &mdash; rank improving 1.5+ places/scan</li>
              <li><span class="signal-hi">↑ Rising</span> &mdash; emerging momentum (0.3&ndash;1.5 places)</li>
              <li><strong>→ Flat</strong> &mdash; no directional signal</li>
              <li><span class="signal-lo">↓ Falling</span> &mdash; momentum fading, even at high rank</li>
              <li><span class="signal-lo">↓↓ Falling fast</span> &mdash; avoid or consider exiting</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="guide-tip" data-i18n-html="guide_modal_tip_3"><strong>Entry setup:</strong> Composite &gt; 0 with ↑ or ↑↑ and a positive Change score. <strong>Exit:</strong> ↓ or ↓↓ even at a high rank &mdash; the sector is topping.</div>
          </div>
        </article>

