            <h2 data-i18n="guide_modal_title_5">Going Deeper</h2>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_5a"><strong>Drill-down</strong> &mdash; select a sector to see its score components across all stored scans. Rising composite + rising Change = sustained acceleration (highest-conviction entry). High composite + falling Change = the sector is topping.</p>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_5b"><strong>Movers</strong> &mdash; rank change between the two most recent scans. Large single-scan jumps need Drill-down confirmation before acting.</p>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_5c"><strong>History</strong> &mdash; all sectors' composite trends over time. Long, smooth uptrends are the entries worth holding; V-shaped reversals are the ones to trade quickly or skip.</p>
            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_5d"><strong>Backtest</strong> &mdash; monthly top-5 rotation strategy vs benchmark, with CAGR, Sharpe, max drawdown, and hit rate. Validates whether the momentum signals would have generated edge historically.</p>
