            <p data-i18n-html="guide_modal_body_6">Google Trends&ndash;based search interest, pulled per region (US direct, EU averaged across DE/FR/GB). Six derived signals per sector:</p>
            <ul data-i18n-html="guide_modal_list_6">
              <li><strong>Momentum</strong> &mdash; trend slope of search interest</li>
              <li><strong>Acceleration</strong> &mdash; is the trend speeding up?</li>
              <li><strong>Range position</strong> &mdash; current vs. 13-week min/max</li>
              <li><strong>Spike</strong> &amp; <strong>Volatility</strong> &mdash; breakout detection and choppiness</li>
              <li><strong>Attention</strong> &mdash; head-to-head comparison across all sectors in the same region</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="guide-tip" data-i18n-html="guide_modal_tip_6"><strong>Info-only by default.</strong> Enable the Sentiment toggle on the leaderboard to blend it into composite rankings at the weight you choose.</div>
